        "Day 8": "Exeter Cathedral guided tour, the Jurassic Coast, Durdle Door. Overnight Bournemouth.",
        "Day 9": "Bournemouth to London via Salisbury, Stonehenge and Windsor Castle.",
        "Day 10": "Return rental car. Depart from London Heathrow."
